<P1>(a) dismiss the Applicant's Summary Judgment Motion;</P1>
<P1>(b) award the Respondent her costs on a substantial indemnity basis; and</P1>
<P1>(c) such further and other grounds as this Honourable Court deems just.</P1></P>
